field2:{"type":"field","size":[392,57],"pos":[66,54],"locked":1,"value":" Easing functions smoothly interpolate from one value to another. They're essential building-blocks of scripted animation! This deck contains an \"ease\" module with a wide variety of easing functions that each take a time (from 0 to 1, inclusive) and numeric values \"a\" and \"b\" to interpolate between. So long as \"a\" and \"b\" conform, they may be scalars, points, or entire polylines."}
